                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted 30th March</hi>, 1846, <hi rend="italic">in the name of Edwin Hodgen, and confined six months</hi>)—I was present at the trial—he is The person.</p>
